snippet.title: DRC OpenWorld Trailer [HD]
snippet.description: Official DemonsAreCrazy's Open World Trailer. Raw gameplay footage taken from open-world part of the game. Hang out with other demons in our open town. Test your survival skill in our pvp combat.  Or gather up and take down raid bosses for awesome rewards!
